:97,"artist":98,"source":9,"url":99,"cover":100},"542058337","大和撫子はあこがれ","遥そら","https://api.obdo.cc/meting/?server=netease&type=url&id=542058337","https://p3.music.126.net/r4KRde43oriYxAgyD8-MOA==/109951163169043939.jpg?param=90y90",{"id":102,"title":103,"artist":104,"source":9,"url":105,"cover":106},"1958727599","明日への扉","高橋李依","https://api.obdo.cc/meting/?server=netease&type=url&id=1958727599","https://p3.music.126.net/fNvDL1E9IX-__sUBPhLAGw==/109951167585364773.jpg?param=90y90",{"id":108,"title":109,"artist":110,"source":9,"url":111,"cover":112},"1818615632","色香水","神山羊","https://api.obdo.cc/meting/?server=netease&type=url&id=1818615632","https://p3.music.126.net/z-GWtONkPJHkPS8G9v55qw==/109951166198068699.jpg?param=90y90",null,{"id":115,"title":116,"body":117,"categories":238,"date":240,"description":241,"draft":242,"extension":243,"hide-info":242,"image":244,"meta":245,"navigation":247,"path":248,"permalink":113,"published":113,"readingTime":249,"recommend":113,"references":113,"seo":254,"sitemap":255,"stem":256,"subtitle":257,"tags":258,"type":260,"updated":113,"__hash__":261},"content/posts/2025/11/cachyos-handheld-chinese-input.md","在 CachyOS Handheld 下恢复 Steam Input 中文输入",{"type":118,"value":119,"toc":230},"minimark",[120,124,128,131,134,137,143,158,168,171,178,186,189,193,204,210,227],[121,122,123],"h2",{"id":123},"前言",[125,126,127],"p",{},"我个人目前在 Steamdeck LCD 上使用的系统并非 SteamOS，而是 CachyOS Handheld，它也是基于 Archlinux 发行的版本，支持 SteamOS 的大部分组件，但是相比 SteamOS 它更为自由一些，软件也是跟随 arch 滚动最新的。",[125,129,130],{},"它不限制系统分区只读，可以自由使用 pacman 和 aur 安装想要的程序。",[125,132,133],{},"不过它毕竟是“仿照” SteamOS 实现的，并且要追求最新组件，所以有些老顽固功能比如 X11 是用 Wayland 替代的，部分应用也不附带，所以经典困扰 Linux 用户的输入法问题又出现了。",[121,135,136],{"id":136},"安装组件",[138,139,140],"alert",{},[125,141,142],{},"只恢复了游戏桌面下的游戏内 Steam Input 输入，且需要强制降级部分组件，请注意！",[125,144,145,146,150,151,154,155],{},"安装",[147,148,149],"code",{"code":149},"ibus","和",[147,152,153],{"code":153},"ibus-pinyin","以及",[147,156,157],{"code":157},"ibus-anthy",[159,160,166],"pre",{"className":161,"code":163,"language":164,"meta":165},[162],"language-bash","paru -S ibus ibus-pinyin ibus-anthy\n","bash","",[147,167,163],{"__ignoreMap":165},[121,169,170],{"id":170},"修改文件",[125,172,173,174,177],{},"打开",[147,175,176],{"code":176},"/usr/share/gamescope-session-plus/gamescope-session-plus","，找到以下行并修改：",[159,179,184],{"className":180,"code":182,"language":183,"meta":165},[181],"language-shell","# Input method support if present\nif command -v /usr/bin/ibus-daemon >/dev/null; then\n\t/usr/bin/ibus-daemon -d -r --panel=disable --emoji-extension=disable # [!code --]\n\t/usr/bin/ibus-daemon -d -r --panel=/usr/lib/kimpanel-ibus-panel --emoji-extension=disable # [!code ++]\nfi\n","shell",[147,185,182],{"__ignoreMap":165},[125,187,188],{},"重启设备，进入游戏桌面后添加中文键盘即可。",[121,190,192],{"id":191},"输入数字","输入数字？",[125,194,195,196,199,200,203],{},"如果你不降级",[147,197,198],{"code":198},"libxkbcommon","组件，会出现中文输入候选输入后为数字的情况，我们可以使用",[147,201,202],{"code":202},"downgrade","组件来帮助我们快速便捷的降级。",[159,205,208],{"className":206,"code":207,"language":183,"meta":165},[181],"# 安装 downgrade 组件\nparu -S downgrade\n# 降级 libxkbcommon 组件\nsudo downgrade libxkbcommon\n",[147,209,207],{"__ignoreMap":165},[125,211,212,213,215,216,219,220,223,224],{},"稍等片刻，就会出现组件版本列表，我们选择",[147,214,198],{"code":198},"的",[147,217,218],{"code":218},"1.11.0","版本，安装完成后还会提示你是否需要把包加入到",[147,221,222],{"code":222},"IgnorePkg","（后续升级也忽略），我们选择",[147,225,226],{"code":226},"y",[125,228,229],{},"等待降级完成后重启设备，再次尝试应该就是中文了。",{"title":165,"searchDepth":231,"depth":231,"links":232},4,[233,235,236,237],{"id":123,"depth":234,"text":123},2,{"id":136,"depth":234,"text":136},{"id":170,"depth":234,"text":170},{"id":191,"depth":234,"text":192},[239],"技术探索","2025-11-24T01:00:00","本文介绍了在 CachyOS Handheld 系统上恢复 Steam Input 中文输入的解决方案。主要步骤包括安装 `ibus`、`ibus-pinyin` 和 `ibus-anthy` 输入法组件，修改 `/usr/share/gamescope-session-plus/gamescope-session-plus` 配置文件，并降级 `libxkbcommon` 组件至 1.11.0 版本以解决中文输入显示为数字的问题。",false,"md","https://cachyos.org/_astro/handheld.DYNjpH4Q_1Y4Eos.webp",{"slots":246},{},true,"/2025/11/cachyos-handheld-chinese-input",{"text":250,"minutes":251,"time":252,"words":253},"3 min read",2.035,122100,407,{"title":116,"description":241},{"loc":248},"posts/2025/11/cachyos-handheld-chinese-input","Arch 是最好用的 Linux 发行版？",[259],"Linux","tech","CuLSfie9Tz3q0QuOhtFxyAVoQo6Oi_jdYLB3pui-4EE",[263,268],{"title":264,"path":265,"stem":266,"date":267,"type":260,"children":-1},"Fedora Cosmic desktop Beta 一日游","/2025/11/fedora-cosmic-beta","posts/2025/11/fedora-cosmic-beta","2025-11-13T20:00:00",{"title":269,"path":270,"stem":271,"date":272,"type":273,"children":-1},"Riddle Joker：剧情不足，人设也不足","/2025/11/riddle-joker","posts/2025/11/riddle-joker","2025-11-24T21:00:00","story",1768477931376]